Package: rsonar
Title: R Code Quality Analysis Inspired by SonarQube
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Damien Dotta", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "damien.dotta@live.fr")
Description: Provides a unified interface for R code quality analysis inspired 
    by SonarQube. Combines lintr (static analysis), styler (code style), 
    covr (test coverage) and goodpractice (best practices) into comprehensive 
    quality reports. Estimates technical debt, detects code smells, and 
    integrates seamlessly into CI/CD pipelines (GitLab CI, GitHub Actions). 
    Produces HTML, JSON and JUnit XML reports suitable for SonarQube ingestion.
